{"tid":741661,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[gym撚入］有冇師兄可以俾啲意見我","createTime":"2018-07-14T00:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T13:50:31.000Z","uid":146358,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b86fb5917f8cda28eb0a6019be4f14ecf940c6ce","tid":741661,"uid":146358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T00:02:52.000Z","msg":"我個人就非常之瘦 身高174但係就重47kg<br />\n經過一個外國朋友說服之後我決定去做gym<br />\n學佢話齋如果怕比人笑 就預咗成世都俾人笑<br />\n寧願俾人笑幾個月 操翻啲肌肉<br />\n<br />\n但係我咩都唔識 所以我想問<br />\n我揀咗去大埔體育會間gym房<br />\n可唔可以話俾我知要做啲咩動作<br />\n要做幾多set 要抖幾耐？<br />\n我自己都有google過所以想上嚟問下意見<br />\n<br />\n同埋食蛋白粉要食邊隻？<br />\n食唔食好？<br />\n<br />\n唔該俾多啲意見我教下我唔好屌我"},{"pid":"27b1193e5d3dfdc081c3443089badaf36644c01d","tid":741661,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T00:14:33.000Z","msg":"係咪對健身動作0知識？？"},{"pid":"6ba9c56c06ad4d4804e380fae3a16f2ec043722a","tid":741661,"uid":146358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27b1193e5d3dfdc081c3443089badaf36644c01d","tid":741661,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T00:14:33.000Z","msg":"係咪對健身動作0知識？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T00:15:00.000Z","msg":"係啊"},{"pid":"eac4cab24ee1f81757470a3d62c794d3643f0268","tid":741661,"uid":84830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ba9c56c06ad4d4804e380fae3a16f2ec043722a","tid":741661,"uid":146358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27b1193e5d3dfdc081c3443089badaf36644c01d","tid":741661,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T00:14:33.000Z","msg":"係咪對健身動作0知識？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T00:15:00.000Z","msg":"係啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T00:27:11.000Z","msg":"咁就搵朋友教你啲基本動作同健身室禮儀，到咁上下先獨自修練"},{"pid":"dcf2f584fb611c416e04c32e183d7612e0c2fbc4","tid":741661,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T00:29:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7738fa9c4940387c064c3aebac8b63cb01e4864","tid"